msg: {LevelDB] fix for StoreQueueCursorLevelDBNoDuplicateTest failure.  When the cursor calls setBatch and then recovering the next batch its expecting the batch to start at lastMsgId + 1 so we were seeing a single duplicate message and since audit was disabled it was delivered.
